{
  "stem": "22979.5",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And also, they warned Hungary what's going on in here to see that the people can escape and not in the transports should revolt because they are going to [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They didn't believe it either.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They didn't believe it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I just mentioned those true brave-- those really true, brave guys who came back alive from hell.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We, too.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, me, too.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But they escaped from the camp, from Birkenau.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So what indication did you have that the war was ending?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because-- first of all, very soon, you know, in-- in 1944 already, in-- before January, before we went to through the death march, we saw already here and there [INAUDIBLE], you know, fire because the Russians were in-- [INAUDIBLE]-- in Krakow.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And Krakow is only 60 kilometers from Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- and, you know, I forgot to mention-- you see I'm already almost done with the camp-- the transports, and Mengele, and the twins.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was not part of them, but I know what was going on.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The, you know, the-- and then, the [? block ?] [? 10 ?] where Renee was, the block where they had Guinea pigs made from-- from the Jewish inmates, where they, you know, all kinds of-- of-- how you say-- experiments on them.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The experiment block, Block 10, where I was first housed in Auschwitz was with Dr.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Clauberg, head of it, who was sentenced, you know, in Nuremberg, and other famous doctors who were assistants of him tortured thousands of Jewish women in different experiments.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then, you had, you know, all kinds of different experiments done even elsewhere in the camp which I don't know about it.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And Dr.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Mengele, the famous Angel of Death, you know, what-- what he did the experiments on twins.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
